Peter Sproule https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Sproule 0 Peter Sproule (born 1947) is an English actor. His roles include a guest appearance on an early episode of Upstairs, Downstairs. He trained at the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art and made his first appearance at the Bristol Old Vic in 1968. Peter_Sproule ( born 1947 ) is an_English_actor .
